snippet.textDisplay: You see the reason this song is winning is because the song doesn’t really seem like it was made in 6 hours. They did a good job putting it together. JME did a great job playing off of everybody’s verses and it just feels like more work was put into this song. The problem with the gift is that it doesn’t really seem like a group out the song together. JJ being the most experienced with music (I don’t really know about S-X) could’ve helped bring everyone together like JME did in merry merry. It feels like the gift was just forced song and they didn’t make much fun out of it. The only time it seemed like they were having fun when they did the knockdown sequence at the end of the song. But oh well, let’s keep merry merry in the lead and merry christmas to those who read this.
